{"type":null,"faqId":37101,"title":"手环是否支持解锁手机？如何用B2解锁P8手机","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、手机解锁功能，目前仅有P8、P8MAX支持，未来将支持Android5.0/EMUI3.1系统的手机。目前华为已经有MATE7、荣耀6Plus、荣耀6、P7、G7、C199等中高端手机有升级Android5.0/EMUI3.1的计划。我们会持续更新软件版本，增加更多好玩的新功能，敬请期待。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、如何解锁：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）手机与B2蓝牙配对成功</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）进入手机“设置”页面，点击“锁屏和密码”选择“智能解锁”，设置图形和数字密码</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（3）进入手机“设置”页面，点击“安全”选择“信任的代理”，开启“智能解锁”功能</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（4）设置成功后，点击“添加用于解锁的设备”，选择B2用于智能解锁</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（5）设置完成后，手机按键锁屏，再次滑动锁屏页面，观察是否存在图形解锁页面</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当B2靠近P8，手机点亮屏幕，手动划屏即可解锁。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2265","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":1218,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,手环解锁,解锁手机,解锁功能,p8解锁","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}